title: Nest Smoke Alarm: Availability and Status
agents: nest
catalog: hw/enviroment
license: GPL
distribution: adams_consuting_github
description:
 This check monitors the reported availability of the Nest Smoke Alarm
 to the central Nest service, and if the current conditions are earning
 a {Nest Leaf}. A leaf indicates energy savings over the baseline power
 use for the current conditions.
 The {Access Token} in the Wato {Host & Services Parameters} is required
 for the agent to query the Nest API.

item:
 The accessibility and operational status of the Nest Smoke Alarm.

inventory:
 One check for each registered Smoke Alarm is created by the inventory

[parameters]
parameters (none): No parameters are required for this check

[configuration]
nest_smoke_co_alarm_default (none): No values are requred for this check

